creditline: Bequest of Margaret McMillan Weber in memory of her mother Katherine Kittridge McMillan
description: Woven designs; three large medallions surrounded by smaller multicolor designs. Trimmed in 1-1/4 in. gold metallic band. Loop and button at top neck. Two loops at each side near waist. Braided multicolor net fring with tassels. Pale green lining. Black front ties.
title: Woman's Formal Vest
